    <item>
      <title>小罗伯特·肯尼迪正在推动对疫苗的大规模调查，尽管他在公开场合保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/health/kennedy-vaccine-safety.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫的命令，卫生部长小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪缓和了对疫苗的公开批评。但在他的部门内部，广泛的研究工作是首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/health/kennedy-vaccine-safety.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 20:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票权决定可能会让田纳西州费耶特县的黑人保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[占田纳西州费耶特县 25% 的黑人居民去年赢得了新的选举地图，从而改变了全白人委员会。他们担心最高法院的裁决可能会威胁到这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/11/us/fayette-county-tennessee-voting-rights.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 19:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
